  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbstractClient.RpcCallable<V>
    The RPC to be executed in AbstractClient.retryRPC(RpcCallable).
    AbstractClient.RpcCallableThrowsAlluxioTException<V>
    Same with AbstractClient.RpcCallable except that this RPC call throws AlluxioTException and is to be executed in AbstractClient.retryRPC(RpcCallableThrowsAlluxioTException).
    AbstractThriftClient.RpcCallable<V,C extends AlluxioService.Client>
    The RPC to be executed in AbstractThriftClient.retryRPC(RpcCallable).
    AbstractThriftClient.RpcCallableThrowsAlluxioTException<V,C extends AlluxioService.Client>
    Same with AbstractThriftClient.RpcCallable except that this RPC call throws AlluxioTException and is to be executed in AbstractThriftClient.retryRPC(RpcCallableThrowsAlluxioTException).

    Interface for a client in the Alluxio system.
